IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. STUDENT-GRADE.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 STUDENT-NAME        PIC A(30).
01 SUBJECT1-MARK       PIC 9(3).
01 SUBJECT2-MARK       PIC 9(3).
01 SUBJECT3-MARK       PIC 9(3).
01 TOTAL-MARKS         PIC 9(3).
01 AVERAGE-MARKS       PIC 9(3)V9(2).
01 GRADE               PIC X.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY "ENTER STUDENT NAME: ".
    ACCEPT STUDENT-NAME.

    DISPLAY "ENTER MARKS FOR SUBJECT 1: ".
    ACCEPT SUBJECT1-MARK.

    DISPLAY "ENTER MARKS FOR SUBJECT 2: ".
    ACCEPT SUBJECT2-MARK.

    DISPLAY "ENTER MARKS FOR SUBJECT 3: ".
    ACCEPT SUBJECT3-MARK.

    COMPUTE TOTAL-MARKS = SUBJECT1-MARK + SUBJECT2-MARK + SUBJECT3-MARK.
    COMPUTE AVERAGE-MARKS = TOTAL-MARKS / 3.

    IF AVERAGE-MARKS >= 90 THEN
        MOVE "A" TO GRADE
    ELSE IF AVERAGE-MARKS >= 75 THEN
        MOVE "B" TO GRADE
    ELSE IF AVERAGE-MARKS >= 60 THEN
        MOVE "C" TO GRADE
    ELSE
        MOVE "F" TO GRADE
    END-IF.

    DISPLAY "STUDENT NAME: " STUDENT-NAME.
    DISPLAY "TOTAL MARKS: " TOTAL-MARKS.
    DISPLAY "AVERAGE MARKS: " AVERAGE-MARKS.
    DISPLAY "GRADE: " GRADE.

    STOP RUN.